commit.title: Helping issue #11659 by leaving only the Cast hack in the grammar.
commit.message:
Helping issue #11659 by leaving only the Cast hack in the grammar.

We move the hack bypassing the interpretation of "'pat" in binders to
comDefinition.ml, and we also fix the exact subterm to which Eval has
to applied in the hack.
